CG019384 Obsolete Denom: $1 Issued: 1963 Last Update: 2023-08-26 Color: Mustard Inserts: 3-Dark Red Mold: SmKey Inlay: R-WHITE Logo: Lake Tahoe Quantity: 21000 Catalog#: N4959 Contributed by: James Campiglia A hoard of 500 of these chips from Barney Chartrand's safe were auctioned on eBay in May, 2016. 

Note that There is a 1st and 2nd issue of this chip and I feel they are reversed. I had a box of each and the ones with the 3 RED/MAROON edge inserts were noticeably more worn than the 3 RED/ORANGE in much newer shape. I do feel that the 3 RED/RAMOON inserts are the first issue and the newer 3 RED/ORANGE inserts are the 2nd issue. Show
